<title>USA: Sterling Software adopts rights plan.</title>
<headline>Sterling Software adopts rights plan.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS, Texas 1996-12-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Sterling Software Inc said on Wednesday it adopted a shareholder rights plan to protect the company and its stockholders against potentially coercive takeover practices.</p>
<p>The company said the action was not taken in response to any pending takeover or proposed change of control.</p>
<p>Rights would be issued to shareholders of record on December 31, the company said.</p>
